28
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,248
Hola a todos.

29
00:03:00,322 --> 00:03:01,516
Hola, amor.

30
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:03,524
- Hola, mamá.
- Perdón por llegar tarde.

31
00:03:03,592 --> 00:03:04,957
No te preocupes. Recién empezamos.

32
00:03:05,594 --> 00:03:06,720
Vamos. Suficiente.

33
00:03:06,795 --> 00:03:09,525
Dios: 27 fibromas.

34
00:03:09,598 --> 00:03:12,260
