680
00:40:22,628 --> 00:40:24,220
Sí.

681
00:40:24,297 --> 00:40:26,492
- Cuídate.
- Hasta luego.

682
00:40:26,566 --> 00:40:27,897
Nos vemos.

683
00:40:32,205 --> 00:40:35,106
Esperemos a que entre.

684
00:40:36,976 --> 00:40:40,002
